Title: Game of Thrones
Original title: Game of Thrones
Year: 2011-2014
Genre: Drama, Fantasy, Adventure
Issued: USA, Bighead Littlehead, Created By, Embassy Films, Generator Entertainment, Home Box Office (HBO)
Directed by: Brian Kirk, Daniel Minahan, Alan Taylor, David Petrarca, David Nutter
Starring: Sean Bean, Nikolaj Coster-Waldau, Lena Headey, Iain Glen, Peter Dinkleydzh, Emilia Clarke, Michelle Fairley, Aidan Gillen, Kit Harington, Mark Addy, Alfie Owen-Allen, Jack Gleeson, Sophie Turner, Maisie Williams, Ron Donakov, Isaac Hempstead-Wright, Jason Momoa, Richard Madden.
Short Description: "Game of Thrones" a new series HBO, based on George RR bestsellers Martin. In a world where summers and winters last for decades, the Westeros crown at stake. Betrayal, lust, intrigue and supernatural forces shake the four corners of the UK - from the scheming south eastern wild lands, to the frozen north and the ancient Wall that protects the kingdom from the darkness behind her. Kings and queens, knights and rebels, liars and noble men vie for power in a bloody battle for the Iron Throne.
